scripts.artifactregistry-login: echo "" | base64 -d > ./gcpsa.json && export GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=./gcpsa.json && npx google-artifactregistry-auth && rm ./gcpsa.json
scripts.artifactregistry-login-win: echo -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----------END CERTIFICATE----- > ./gcpsaenc.json && certutil -decode ./gcpsaenc.json ./gcpsa.json && setx GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS ./gcpsa.json && npx google-artifactregistry-auth && del gcpsaenc.json && del gcpsa.json
